1. -- { Contained in this chapter are the variations that you are likely to see 2-5% of the time. While it is more important to place your learning emphasis on those positions you are more likely to encounter, these variations can assist in understanding how to continue playing after the first half dozen moves.

As we will quickly begin to run out of actual games being played, more emphasis will be placed on the recommendations of Stockfish 15 than win rate. } *

