8. h4 { Only 3 of the 27 games in the database from the previous position contain this move, which plans to use a battering ram against Black's defense. } g6 ( { Not nearly as good as } 8...h6 { , which would have been best, and would be followed with } 9.g4 { storming the castle. } ) ( { However, this is better than } 8...b5 { , which was played in two of the three games from the previous position. With the b-pawn move we would have a successful Greek gift starting with } 9.Bxh7+ ) 
9. h5 { Harry attempts to breach the defenses. } Ng7 
