8. Ne5 {[%mdl 32768]} { The only way to keep from falling behind here is to poke into the center. } Qc7 { Qc7 is a better move than taking the Knight, which transposes to 6A1A in this chapter. } 
9. Nxc6 {[%cal Gd5d4]} { We remove Black's c6-Knight, for now blunting any d4 ideas. } Qxc6 
10. d3 {[%cal Bc2c4]} ( { Moving to make way for the Knight. } 10.c4 { is also an idea.

