Prior to Black's move the win rate in this position was 51% - 43%. As it turns out, Black's most commonly played move offers the best win percentage of all played moves and knocks that down to 44%-51%.

Of interest is the fact that Stockfish 14 offered a valuation of +0.7 before this move, and now +1.0 following the move. The bottom line is that we should not get too caught up in specific numbers in search for that elusive silver bullet. Understanding the best moves is key to success in this, as well as every other variation. } 
