[Event "The Classical Bird for Club Players"]
[White "Continuations Game Examples"]
[Black "Introduction"]
[Date "2023.08.15"]
[Result "*"]
[SourceTitle "https://www.chessable.com/variation/28641074"]

{ This collection of game examples includes those variations where we went beyond move 6. It is interesting to note the dearth of actual games in the database when only four additional moves have been made.

This speaks to the lack of heavy theory surrounding this opening, as very early in the game at least one player is likely to no longer be in familiar territory unless a transposition has occurred - and games in this chapter that begin with Bird's Opening comprise only about a third of the whole.

I highly recommend going through some of these games. They show successful and unsuccessful ideas, and also highlight the fact that in our rating range tactics can be in the air if one is looking for them.

Welcome to the Wild West. } 1. -- *

