[Event "The Classical Bird for Club Players"]
[White "Middlegame Play Examples"]
[Black "Introduction"]
[Date "2023.08.15"]
[Result "*"]
[SourceTitle "https://www.chessable.com/variation/29364093"]

{ This final collection of games contains continuations from the Middlegame Play chapter. As we have delved deeper into the opening with those variations, there are far fewer games that stem from where we left off each one - many variations have no games in the database.

The fact that fifteen or so moves into the game we are left oftentimes with unique positions that have no paper trail is a testament to the idea that this is not a well explored opening. Who knows, perhaps someday a variation will have your name associated with it, as opposed to the 2... Nc6 3... Nf6 with 4... Bd7 and 5... e6 variation! } 1. -- *

